OL,5,G2215 FIFA WC2026: Argentina v C. Verde
OL,6,     FArgentina v Cape Verde (Kick-off
OL,7,     F11.00pm). Coverage of the
OL,8,     Fround-of-32 match at Miami Stadium
OL,9,     Fin the USA. Reigning champions
OL,10,     FArgentina topped Group J with a
OL,11,     Fgame to spare after talisman
OL,12,     FLionel Messi scored all five of
OL,13,     Fhis team's goals in wins over
OL,14,     FAlgeria and Austria. The progress
OL,15,     Fof Cape Verde is arguably the
OL,16,     Fstory of the tournament so far,
OL,17,     Fwith the unfancied and unheralded
OL,18,     Fminnows reaching this stage at the
OL,19,     Ffirst attempt, courtesy of draws
OL,20,     Fagainst Spain, Uruguay and Saudi
OL,21,     FArabia
