OL,5,G0200 FIFA WC2026: Colombia v Ghana
OL,6,     FColombia v Ghana (Kick-off
OL,7,     F2.30am). Coverage of the final
OL,8,     Fround-of-32 match, held at Kansas
OL,9,     FCity Stadium in the USA. Colombia
OL,10,     Fwon Group K with seven points,
OL,11,     Fcourtesy of wins against DR Congo
OL,12,     Fand Uzbekistan, and a goalless
OL,13,     Fdraw with Portugal. Ghana
OL,14,     Fimpressed at times in the group
OL,15,     Fstage, holding England to a
OL,16,     Fgoalless draw and taking the lead
OL,17,     Fagainst Croatia, before succumbing
OL,18,     Fto a 2-1 defeat that left them
OL,19,     Fthird in Group L
